sentences: She was born in Tjøme, and made her concert debut in Oslo in 1940.
She lectured at the Norwegian Academy of Music from 1973 to 1991.
She was awarded the Harriet Cohen International Music Award in 1966, and the King's Medal of Merit in gold in 1986.
